Description: Two fragments of a papyrus document; one blank, one with 8 lines of Coptic text written against the fibres (verso), 1 line written along the fibres (recto). EA 75337, 75336, 75335, 75334 are mounted together.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380762) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380762)
